From 187a911a53a42d7e2ecf04b12c3a42f5e87a8052 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LordAfterEight <elias@stettmayer.de>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 20:10:33 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] hw/arm: add STM32H745 SoC and carrier machine

Introduce stm32h745-carrier for a custom STM32H745BIT6 board:
Cortex-M7, 2 MiB flash, internal SRAMs, 64 MiB FMC SDRAM window,
minimal H7 RCC/GPIO/USART1 for Rust ArmOS bring-up.
